BODYPUMP is a fast-paced, barbell-based workout that uses a combination of motivating music and scientifically proven moves to help you get lean, toned and fit.
Vinyasa is a style of Yoga characterized by stringing postures together so that you move from one to another. Seamlessly, using breath. This class is the essential body and mind experience.

Barre focuses on strengthening and tightening the hips, glutes, thighs, and corewhile improving posture. The truth is, barre workouts are hard. The challenge of this class is that it target muscles in specific ways that aren't necessarily used in everyday movement.

BODYCOMBAT is a high-energy martial arts-inspired workout that is totally non-contact. Punch and kick your way to fitness in a class. No experience needed. Learn moves from Karate, Taekwondo, Boxing, Muay Thai, Capoeira and Kung Fu. Release stress, have a blast and feel like a champ. Bring your best fighter attitude and leave inhibitions at the door.
A fantastic dynamic full body stretch and deep core workout which hones in on postural muscle groups and develops overall toning
BODYATTACK is a high-energy fitness class that combines athletic movements like running, lunging and jumping with strength exercises like push ups and squats.

Come into SW7 with one of the Active Lifestyles Team as we take you through the basic technique of the most common weightlifting exercises from Bench Press to Squatting, well have you leaving these sessions equipped with the knowledge to step into the main gym and complete basic workouts to build your strength!

WOD = Workout of the Day Step into SW7 and push yourself to the limit with our Active Lifestyles Team as they take you through Conditioning workouts via AMRAPs, EMOMs, Chippers and many more conditioning workouts using a combination of Weightlifting, Bodyweight & Machines such as the Assault Bike & Ski Ergs!
We take you through full body workouts using a combination of bodyweight, dumbbell, kettlebell & barbell exercises to help build functional strength so you can live day to day STRONG!
